Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion

Class InsertionServiceRegistry

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion.InsertionServiceRegistry
public class InsertionServiceRegistry extends Object
Registry for managing Insertion services for various UI components.

This class provides a centralized way to register and retrieve insertion services based on specific ComponentType implementations. It ensures that the correct service is used for handling UI interactions related to data insertion.

Uses a ConcurrentHashMap to support thread-safe access and modifications.
